reviewText: Such a stupid waste of of time. There are much better GGW dvds out there. Don't waste your money on this one.
Not as good as I thought it would be.

This DVD is hot. It lets us in on the real Mardi Gras. I think GGW should follow up the formula and show us some other global hot spots .. like Rio Carnival .. or the crazy Thailand beach party scene!! ... Check out "Wild Girls Thailand" (ASIN:B000F6YVRW) for some real hot beach, bikini action.
